"我们推荐你的浏览器保持更新。新版本的浏览器一直在改进JavaScript和渲染的性能。"
"使用老版本浏览器时大型系统会出现戏剧性的性能问题。我们乐于在此问题上为您提供"
"咨询。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:503
msgid "Community"
msgstr "社区"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:506
msgid ""
"OTRS has a large user community. Users and developers discuss OTRS and "
"exchange information on related issues through the <link linkend="
"\"additional-resources\">mailing-lists</link>.  You can use the mailing "
"lists to discuss installation, configuration, usage, localization and "
"development of OTRS. You can report software bugs in our <link linkend="
"\"additional-resources\">bug tracking system</link>."
msgstr ""
"OTRS拥有一个大型的用户社区。用户和开发人员通过<link linkend=\"additional-"
"resources\">邮件列表</link>讨论OTRS并交换相关问题的信息。你可以使用邮件列表来"
"讨论OTRS的安装、配置、使用、本地化和开发方面的问题。你也可以通过我们的<link "
"linkend=\"additional-resources\">bug跟踪系统</link>报告软件BUG。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:515
