"活动对话框中包含了采购涉及的供应商、价格与发货日期字段以及状态字段选项 “生成"
"订单”。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:547
msgid "\"Shipment received\" (AD6)"
msgstr "“货品收到” (AD6)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:549
msgid ""
"An activity for the mail room with a field for the Date of receipt and the "
"Status field with the option \"Shipment received\"."
msgstr ""
"此活动需要为收发室添加一个收到日期的字段，还需要一个状态字段选项“货品收到”。"

