"                Match => 'Raw',\n"
"            },\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"},\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2502
msgid "Let's look at the condition configuration in detail."
msgstr "让我们看看这个条件配置的详细信息。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2505
msgid "Type (Condition)"
msgstr "类型（条件间）"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2507
msgid ""
"Specifies the way the different condition elements are connected to each "
"other. Possible values:"
msgstr "指定不同的条件元素互相连接的方式，可能的值有："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2512
msgid ""
"'and': This is the default. All conditions must be met for the transition to "
"take effect."
msgstr "‘与’：这是默认类型。要使转换生效必须满足所有的条件。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2518
msgid "'or': At least one condition must match."
msgstr "‘或’：至少需要满足一个条件。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2523
msgid "'xor': Exactly one condition must match, not more."
msgstr "‘异或’：必须恰好满足一个条件，不能满足多个条件。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2530
msgid "Cond1"
msgstr "Cond1"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2532
msgid ""
"This is the name of an example condition. It can be freely chosen.  "
"Conditions are evaluated in sorted order."
msgstr "这是示例条件的名称。可以随便选择条件名称。条件按排好的顺序评估。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2537
msgid "Type (Cond)"
msgstr "类型（条件内字段）"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2539
msgid ""
"Specifies the way how the individual field tests of this condition are "
"connected to each other. Possible values:"
msgstr "指定这个条件内单个字段的测试结果互相连接的方式，可能的值有："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2544
msgid ""
"'and': This is the default. All field tests must match for this condition to "
"match."
msgstr "‘与’：这是默认类型。这个条件内的所有字段测试结果必须都匹配。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2550
msgid "'or': At least one field test must match."
msgstr "‘或’：至少需要匹配一个字段。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2555
msgid "'xor': Exactly one field test must match, not more."
msgstr "‘异或’：必须恰好匹配一个字段的测试结果，不能匹配多个。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2564
msgid ""
"Specifies the particular fields whose values should be tested. From our "
"example:"
msgstr "指定要测试其值的特殊字段。在我们的例子中："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2569
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Fields => {\n"
"    StateID => {\n"
"        Type  => 'String',\n"
"        Match => '1',\n"
"    },\n"
"                        "
msgstr ""
"Fields => {\n"
"    StateID => {\n"
"        Type  => 'String',\n"
"        Match => '1',\n"
"    },\n"
"                        "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2578
msgid "StateID"
msgstr "状态ID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2580
msgid "Example of a field name. The following ticket fields can be used:"
msgstr "字段名的例子。可以使用下列工单字段："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2584
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    Title\n"
"    State\n"
"    StateID\n"
"    Priority\n"
"    PriorityID\n"
"    Lock\n"
"    LockID\n"
"    Queue\n"
"    QueueID\n"
"    Customer\n"
"    CustomerID\n"
"    CustomerNo\n"
"    CustomerUserID\n"
"    Owner\n"
"    OwnerID\n"
"    Type\n"
"    TypeID\n"
"    SLA\n"
"    SLAID\n"
"    Service\n"
"    ServiceID\n"
"    Responsible\n"
"    ResponsibleID\n"
"    DynamicField_$FieldName # for all DynamicFields\n"
"                        "
msgstr ""
"    Title\n"
"    State\n"
"    StateID\n"
"    Priority\n"
"    PriorityID\n"
"    Lock\n"
"    LockID\n"
"    Queue\n"
"    QueueID\n"
"    Customer\n"
"    CustomerID\n"
"    CustomerNo\n"
"    CustomerUserID\n"
"    Owner\n"
"    OwnerID\n"
"    Type\n"
"    TypeID\n"
"    SLA\n"
"    SLAID\n"
"    Service\n"
"    ServiceID\n"
"    Responsible\n"
"    ResponsibleID\n"
"    DynamicField_$FieldName # for all DynamicFields\n"
"                        "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2611
msgid ""
"When testing a field with 'ID' (like SLAID), the database ID of the field "
"will be used for testing, for other fields (like SLA) the actual value is "
"used for testing."
msgstr ""
"当测试一个含有‘ID’（如SLAID）的字段时，这个字段的数据库ID将用于测试，而其它字"
"段则使用实际值来测试。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2619
msgid "Determines the kind of field testing. Possible values:"
msgstr "确定字段测试的类型，可能的值有："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2624
msgid ""
"'String': Compares the field value with the string specified in 'Match'. "
"Matches if they are exactly the same."
msgstr ""
"‘String字符串’：比较字段值和在'Match'中指定的字符串，如果完全相同就是匹配的。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2630
msgid ""
"'Hash': Compares the field value (hash) with the hash specified in 'Match'. "
"All hash values must be the same."
msgstr ""
"'Hash哈希'：比较字段值的哈希值和在'Match'中指定的哈希值。所有的哈希值必须一致"
"才是匹配的。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2636
msgid ""
"'Array': Compares the field value (array) with the array specified in "
"'Match'. Both lists must be the same."
msgstr ""
"'Array数组'：比较字段值的数组和在'Match'中指定的数组。两个数据的清单值必须一"
"致才是匹配的。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2642
msgid ""
"'Regex': The field value can be tested with a regular expression. It is "
"important that 'Match' contains <emphasis>qr{}xms</emphasis> as a base "
"condition. Between the braces the actual regular expression can be noted."
msgstr ""
"'Regex正则表达式'：使用一个正则表达式来测试字段值，重点注意的是'Match'包含"
"<emphasis>qr{}xms</emphasis>作为基本条件。实际的正则表达式是在大括号中间。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2650
msgid ""
"'Module': Allows you to use a perl module for condition checking. If it "
"returns 1, the check was positive. You can find an example module in "
"<filename>Kernel/System/ProcessManagement/TransitionValidation/ValidateDemo."
"pm</filename>."
msgstr ""
"'Module模块'：允许你使用一个Perl模块来进行条件检查。如果模块返回1，检查是匹配"
"的。你可以在文件<filename>Kernel/System/ProcessManagement/"
"TransitionValidation/ValidateDemo.pm</filename>中找到一个示例模块。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2665
msgid ""
"Transition Actions are actions which can be triggered after successfully "
"applied transitions (when a process ticket moves from one activity to "
"another). These Transition Actions can be used to perform different changes "
"on the ticket, e. g.  change the Queue or the Owner of the ticket, and you "
"can also create your own Transition Actions to perform other complex changes."
msgstr ""
"转换操作是成功应用转换后触发的操作（当一个流程工单从一个活动移动到另一活动"
"时）。这些转换操作用来对工单执行不同的变更，如变更工单的队列或所有者，你还可"
"以创建你自己的转换操作来执行其它的复杂变更。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2672
msgid "Transition Action configuration"
msgstr "转换操作配置"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2678
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Queue Move',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Queue  => 'Junk',\n"
"            UserID => 123,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Queue Move',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Queue  => 'Junk',\n"
"            UserID => 123,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2694
msgid "The name of the Transition Action."
msgstr "转换操作的名称。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2698
msgid "Module"
msgstr "模块"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2700
msgid "Specifies the Perl module to be used."
msgstr "指定使用的Perl模块。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2704
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-configuration.xml:265
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-configuration.xml:457
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-configuration.xml:817
msgid "Config"
msgstr "配置"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2706
msgid ""
"This parameter contains all settings which are required for the module. Its "
"content depends on the particular Transition Action module which is used. "
"Please see the documentation of the individual modules for details. In our "
"example, only the Queue must be specified. Nevertheless we are also sending "
"UserID parameter, by using the UserID parameter. The transition action will "
"be executed impersonating the user with the given UserID."
msgstr ""
"这个参数包含模块所需的所有设置。它的内容取决于使用的特定的转换操作模块。请参"
"阅单独的模块文档以了解详细信息。在我们的示例中，只是必须指定队列。不过我们还"
"需发送UserID参数。转换操作将使用给定的UserID来模拟用户执行。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2714
msgid ""
"The use of UserID inside the \"Config\" parameter of a Transition Action is "
"accepted by all Transition Actions (since OTRS 3.2.4). In this example it "
"could be particularly important if the user that triggers the Transition "
"does not have permissions to move the ticket to the queue 'Junk', while the "
"user with the UserID 123 might have."
msgstr ""
"转换操作在“配置”参数中UserID的用法可在所有的转换操作中使用（从OTRS 3.2.4版本"
"之后）。在本示例中特别重要的是触发转换操作的用户（也就是UserID为123的用户）有"
"没有移动工单到队列'Junk'的权限。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2722
msgid "Reusing Transition Action modules"
msgstr "重复使用转换操作模块"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2724
msgid ""
"To use Transition Action modules multiple times, just specify several "
"Transition Actions in your configuration. Example:"
msgstr "要重复使用转换操作模块，只需在配置中指定多个转换操作。例如："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2729
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    $Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"        'TA1' => {\n"
"            Name   => 'Queue Move Junk',\n"
"            Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"            Config => {\n"
"                Queue => 'Junk',\n"
"            },\n"
"        },\n"
"        'TA2' => {\n"
"            Name   => 'Queue Move Raw',\n"
"            Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"            Config => {\n"
"                Queue => 'Raw',\n"
"            },\n"
"        },\n"
"    };\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"    $Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"        'TA1' => {\n"
"            Name   => 'Queue Move Junk',\n"
"            Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"            Config => {\n"
"                Queue => 'Junk',\n"
"            },\n"
"        },\n"
"        'TA2' => {\n"
"            Name   => 'Queue Move Raw',\n"
"            Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"            Config => {\n"
"                Queue => 'Raw',\n"
"            },\n"
"        },\n"
"    };\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2748
msgid ""
"Here the same module is used to move a process ticket into the 'Raw' queue, "
"and another time to move it into the junk queue. The Transition Action which "
"must be used for a particular Transition is determined from the 'Path' "
"setting of the Process configuration."
msgstr ""
"这里使用了同一个模块来移到一个流程工单到队列'Raw'，还有移到队列'junk'。一个特"
"定转换使用的转换操作由流程配置中的‘路径’设置来确定。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2755
msgid "Available Transition Actions"
msgstr "可用的转换操作"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2757
msgid ""
"OTRS comes with several Transition Actions that can be used in your "
"processes.  Here you can find their documentation and how they need to be "
"configured."
msgstr ""
"OTRS自带了多个可在你的流程中使用的转换操作。在这里你可以找到它们的文档以及需"
"要如何配置它们。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2764
msgid "Sets one or more dynamic fields at a process ticket. Example:"
msgstr "在一个流程工单中设置一个或多个动态字段，示例："

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2767
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set DynamicField MasterSlave to Master and Approved to 1',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::DynamicFieldSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            MasterSlave => 'Master',\n"
"            Approved    => '1',\n"
"\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set DynamicField MasterSlave to Master and Approved to 1',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::DynamicFieldSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            MasterSlave => 'Master',\n"
"            Approved    => '1',\n"
"\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2782
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3128
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3159
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3190
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3221
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3252
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3286
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3321
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3354
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3389
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3417
msgid "'Name' specifies the name of the configured TransitionAction."
msgstr "‘Name名称’指定配置的转换操作的名称。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2785
msgid ""
"'MasterSlave' and 'Approved' are given as examples of DynamicField names.  "
"The values of the fields ('Master' and '1') will be set by this "
"TransitionAction."
msgstr ""
"‘MasterSlave主从’和‘Approved通过审批’就像动态字段名称一样指定，这个转换操作设"
"置它们的值为（'Master' 和 '1'）。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2794
msgid ""
"Creates an article and can be used to create notes or email replies. Example:"
msgstr "创建一个信件，并用于创建备注或邮件回复。"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2797
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Article Create Note Internal',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketArticleCreate',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            ArticleType      => 'note-internal',                                        # note-external|phone|fax|sms|...\n"
"                                                                                        #   excluding any email type\n"
"            SenderType       => 'agent',                                                # agent|system|customer\n"
"            ContentType      => 'text/plain; charset=ISO-8859-15',                      # or optional Charset & MimeType (e.g. 'text/html; charset=UTF-8')\n"
"            Subject          => 'some short description',                               # required\n"
"            Body             => 'the message text',                                     # required\n"
"            HistoryType      => 'OwnerUpdate',                                          # EmailCustomer|Move|AddNote|PriorityUpdate|WebRequestCustomer|...\n"
"            HistoryComment   => 'Some free text!',\n"
"            From             => 'Some Agent <email@example.com>',                       # not required but useful\n"
"            To               => 'Some Customer A <customer-a@example.com>',             # not required but useful\n"
"            Cc               => 'Some Customer B <customer-b@example.com>',             # not required but useful\n"
"            ReplyTo          => 'Some Customer B <customer-b@example.com>',             # not required\n"
"            InReplyTo        => '<asdasdasd.12@example.com>',                           # not required but useful\n"
"            References       => '<asdasdasd.1@example.com> <asdasdasd.12@example.com>', # not required but useful\n"
"            NoAgentNotify    => 0,                                                      # if you don't want to send agent notifications\n"
"            AutoResponseType => 'auto reply',                                           # auto reject|auto follow up|auto reply/new ticket|auto remove\n"
"\n"
"            ForceNotificationToUserID   => [ 1, 43, 56 ],                               # if you want to force somebody\n"
"            ExcludeNotificationToUserID => [ 43, 56 ],\n"
"                 # if you want full exclude somebody from notifications,\n"
"                 # will also be removed in To: line of article,\n"
"                 # higher prio as ForceNotificationToUserID\n"
"            ExcludeMuteNotificationToUserID => [ 43, 56 ],\n"
"                 # the same as ExcludeNotificationToUserID but only the\n"
"                 # sending gets muted, agent will still shown in To:\n"
"                 # line of article\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2835
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2973
msgid ""
"'Name' specifies the name of the configured TransitionAction. It can be "
"freely chosen, but should reflect the purpose of the configured action."
msgstr ""
"‘Name名称’指定这个转换操作的名称。可以随意选择，但名称最好能体现转换操作的用"
"途。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2839
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3032
msgid ""
"'ArticleType' defines the type of the article to be created. Possible "
"values: phone, fax, sms, webrequest, note-internal, note-external and note-"
"report."
msgstr ""
"‘ArticleType信件类型’定义创建的信件的类型。可能的值有：电话、传真、短信、WEB"
"请求、备注-内部、备注-外部和备注-报告。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2844
msgid ""
"'SenderType' defines the sender type of the article. Possible values: agent, "
"system, customer."
msgstr ""
"‘SenderType发件人类型’定义信件发件人的类型。可能的值有：服务人员、系统、客"
"户。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2848
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3041
msgid ""
"'ContentType' defines the content type of the article. Possible values: "
"'text/plain; charset=ISO-8859-15' or any other valid charset and mime type."
msgstr ""
"‘ContentType内容类型’定义信件的内容类型。可能的值有：‘text/plain; "
"charset=ISO-8859-15纯文本’或其它有效的字符集和MIME类型。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2852
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3045
msgid "'Subject' defines the article title. Mandatory."
msgstr "‘Subject主题’定义信件主题，必填。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2855
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3048
msgid "'Body' defines the article content. Mandatory."
msgstr "‘Body正文’定义信件的内容，必填。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2858
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3051
msgid ""
"'HistoryType' defines the type of the history entry. Possible values: "
"AddNote, ArchiveFlagUpdate, Bounce, CustomerUpdate, EmailAgent, "
"EmailCustomer, EscalationResponseTimeNotifyBefore, "
"EscalationResponseTimeStart, EscalationResponseTimeStop, "
"EscalationSolutionTimeNotifyBefore, EscalationSolutionTimeStart, "
"EscalationSolutionTimeStop, EscalationUpdateTimeNotifyBefore, "
"EscalationUpdateTimeStart, EscalationUpdateTimeStop, FollowUp, Forward, "
"Lock, LoopProtection, Merged, Misc, Move, NewTicket, OwnerUpdate, "
"PhoneCallAgent, PhoneCallCustomer, PriorityUpdate, Remove, "
"ResponsibleUpdate, SendAgentNotification, SendAnswer, SendAutoFollowUp, "
"SendAutoReject, SendAutoReply, SendCustomerNotification, ServiceUpdate, "
"SetPendingTime, SLAUpdate, StateUpdate, Subscribe, SystemRequest, "
"TicketDynamicFieldUpdate, TicketLinkAdd, TicketLinkDelete, TimeAccounting, "
"TypeUpdate, Unlock, Unsubscribe, WebRequestCustomer."
msgstr ""
"‘HistoryType历史类型’定义历史条目的类型。可能的值有：添加备注、归档标志更新、"
"退回、客户更新、服务人员邮件、客户邮件、升级响应时间通知之前、升级响应时间通"
"知开始、升级响应时间结束、升级解决时间通知之前、升级解决时间通知开始、升级解"
"决时间结束、升级更新时间之前、升级更新时间开始、升级更新时间结束、跟进、转"
"发、锁定、循环保护、合并、杂项、转换、新工单、所有者更新、服务人员电话、客户"
"电话、优先级更新、移除、负责人更新、发送服务人员通知、发送答复、发送自动跟"
"进、发送自动拒绝、发送自动回复、发送客户通知、服务更新、设置挂起时间、SLA更"
"新、状态更新、关注、系统请求、工单动态字段更新、添加工单链接、删除工单链接、"
"工时管理、类型更新、解锁、取消关注、客户WEB请求。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2874
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3067
msgid "'HistoryComment' defines the content of the history entry."
msgstr "‘HistoryComment历史注释’定义历史条目的内容。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2877
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3070
msgid ""
"'From', 'To', 'Cc' and 'ReplyTo' take email addresses in the notation "
"specified above."
msgstr ""
"'From发件人'、 'To收件人'、 'Cc抄送' 和 'ReplyTo回复'使用上面指定格式的邮件地"
"址。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2881
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3074
msgid "'InReplyTo' and 'References' take email message IDs."
msgstr "‘InReplyTo作为答复’和‘References参考’使用邮件消息ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2884
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3077
msgid ""
"'NoAgentNotify' - if set to 1, the email notification of the Agent will not "
"be sent."
msgstr ""
"‘NoAgentNotify无服务人员通知’-如果设置为1，不会发送服务人员的邮件通知。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2888
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3081
msgid ""
"'AutoResponseType' can take the following values: auto follow up, auto "
"reject, auto remove, auto reply, auto reply/new ticket."
msgstr ""
"‘AutoResponseType自动响应类型’可以使用下列的值：自动跟进、自动拒绝、自动移"
"除、自动回复、自动回复/新工单。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2892
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3085
msgid ""
"'ForceNotificationToUserID', 'ExcludeNotificationToUserID', "
"'ExcludeMuteNotificationToUserID' can take a list of UserIDs that are either "
"always notified, not notified or listed as notified but not actually sent a "
"notification email."
msgstr ""
"‘ForceNotificationToUserID强制发送通知给UserID’、‘ExcludeNotificationToUserID"
"为UserID排除通知’、‘ExcludeMuteNotificationToUserID为UserID排除静音通知’可以"
"使用的UserID列表，给这些UserID的用户要么始终发送通知、不发送通知，要么加入发"
"送清单但并不发送通知邮件。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2901
msgid ""
"Creates a ticket with an article, the new ticket can be linked with process "
"ticket. Example:"
msgstr "创建一个有信件的工单，这个新工单能够链接到流程工单。例如："

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2905
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Ticket Create',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketCreate',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"\n"
"            # ticket required:\n"
"            Title         => 'Some Ticket Title',\n"
"            Queue         => 'Raw',              # or QueueID => 123,\n"
"            Lock          => 'unlock',\n"
"            Priority      => '3 normal',         # or PriorityID => 2,\n"
"            State         => 'new',              # or StateID => 5,\n"
"            CustomerID    => '123465',\n"
"            CustomerUser  => 'customer@example.com',\n"
"            OwnerID       => 'someuserlogin',    # or OwnerID => 123,\n"
"\n"
"            # ticket optional:\n"
"            TN              => $TicketObject->TicketCreateNumber(), # optional\n"
"            Type            => 'Incident',            # or TypeID => 1, not required\n"
"            Service         => 'Service A',           # or ServiceID => 1, not required\n"
"            SLA             => 'SLA A',               # or SLAID => 1, not required\n"
"            ResponsibleID   => 123,                   # not required\n"
"            ArchiveFlag     => 'y',                   # (y|n) not required\n"
"            PendingTime     => '2011-12-23 23:05:00', # optional (for pending states)\n"
"            PendingTimeDiff => 123 ,                  # optional (for pending states)\n"
"\n"
"            # article required:\n"
"            ArticleType      => 'note-internal',                        # note-external|phone|fax|sms|...\n"
"                                                                        #   excluding any email type\n"
"            SenderType       => 'agent',                                # agent|system|customer\n"
"            ContentType      => 'text/plain; charset=ISO-8859-15',      # or optional Charset & MimeType (e.g. 'text/html; charset=UTF-8')\n"
"            Subject          => 'some short description',               # required\n"
"            Body             => 'the message text',                     # required\n"
"            HistoryType      => 'OwnerUpdate',                          #\n"
"            EmailCustomer|Move|AddNote|PriorityUpdate|WebRequestCustomer|...\n"
"            HistoryComment   => 'Some free text!',\n"
"\n"
"            # article optional:\n"
"            From             => 'Some Agent <email@example.com>',       # not required but useful\n"
"            To               => 'Some Customer A <customer-a@example.com>', # not required but useful\n"
"            Cc               => 'Some Customer B <customer-b@example.com>', # not required but useful\n"
"            ReplyTo          => 'Some Customer B <customer-b@example.com>', # not required\n"
"            MessageID        => '<asdasdasd.123@example.com>',          # not required but useful\n"
"            InReplyTo        => '<asdasdasd.12@example.com>',           # not required but useful\n"
"            References       => '<asdasdasd.1@example.com> <asdasdasd.12@example.com>', # not required but useful\n"
"            NoAgentNotify    => 0,                                      # if you don't want to send agent notifications\n"
"            AutoResponseType => 'auto reply'                            # auto reject|auto follow up|auto reply/new ticket|auto remove\n"
"\n"
"            ForceNotificationToUserID   => [ 1, 43, 56 ],               # if you want to force somebody\n"
"            ExcludeNotificationToUserID => [ 43,56 ],                   # if you want full exclude somebody from notifications,\n"
"                                                                        # will also be removed in To: line of article,\n"
"                                                                        # higher prio as ForceNotificationToUserID\n"
"            ExcludeMuteNotificationToUserID => [ 43,56 ],               # the same as ExcludeNotificationToUserID but only the\n"
"                                                                        # sending gets muted, agent will still shown in To:\n"
"                                                                        # line of article\n"
"            TimeUnit                        => 123\n"
"\n"
"            # other:\n"
"            DynamicField_NameX => $Value,\n"
"            LinkAs => $LinkType,                                        # Normal, Parent, Child, etc. (respective original ticket)\n"
"            UserID => 123,                                              # optional, to override the UserID from the logged user\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2977
msgid "'Title' The ticket title."
msgstr "‘Title标题’工单的标题。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2980
msgid ""
"'Queue' or 'QueueID' specifies the name or id of the queue to be used in the "
"new ticket."
msgstr "‘Queue队列’或‘QueueID’指定用于新工单的队列名称或ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2984
msgid "'Lock' or 'LockID' sets the lock status of the ticket."
msgstr "‘Lock锁定’或‘LockID’设置工单的锁定状态。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2987
msgid ""
"'Priority' or 'PriorityID' specifies the name or id of the priority to be "
"used in the new ticket."
msgstr "‘Priority优先级’或‘PriorityID’在新工单中指定优先级的名称或ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2991
msgid ""
"'State' or 'StateID' specifies the name or id of the state to be used in the "
"new ticket."
msgstr "‘State状态’或‘StateID’在新工单中指定状态的名称或ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2995
msgid "'CustomerID', the customer id to be set for the new ticket."
msgstr "‘CustomerID客户ID’，为新工单设置客户ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2998
msgid ""
"'CustomerUser', the login of the customer that will be assigned in the "
"ticket."
msgstr "‘CustomerUser客户联系人’，分配给工单的客户登录名。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3002
msgid ""
"'Owner' or 'OwnerID', specifies the login or id of the agent that will be "
"the new ticket owner."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3005
msgid "'TN', custom number for the new ticket."
msgstr "‘TN’，新工单的客户编号。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3008
msgid ""
"'Type' or 'TypeID' specifies the name or id of the ticket type to be used in "
"the new ticket."
msgstr "‘Type类型’或‘TypeID’，指定用于新工单的工单类型名称或ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3012
msgid ""
"'Service' or 'ServiceID' specifies the name or id of the service to be used "
"in the new ticket."
msgstr "‘Service服务’或‘ServiceID’，指定用于新工单的服务名称或ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3016
msgid ""
"'SLA' or 'SLAID' specifies the name or id of the SLA to be used in the new "
"ticket."
msgstr "‘SLA’或‘SLAID’，指定用于新工单的SLA名称或ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3020
msgid ""
"'ResponsibleID', the ID of the agent that will be the new ticket responsible."
msgstr "‘ResponsibleID负责人ID’，新工单负责人的服务人员ID。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3023
msgid ""
"'PendingTime', a predefined date to set the Ticket Pending Times, when the "
"ticket state belongs to a pending state type."
msgstr ""
"‘PendingTime挂起时间’，预先定义的当工单状态属于一种挂起状态类型时工单的挂起时"
"间。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3027
msgid ""
"'PendingTimeDiff', a dynamically date (expressed in seconds from current "
"date/time) to set the Ticket Pending Times, when the ticket state belongs to "
"a pending state type."
msgstr ""
"‘PendingTimeDiff挂起时间差’，当工单状态属于一种挂起状态类型时，给工单挂起时间"
"设置一个动态时间（从当前时间按秒表示）。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3037
msgid ""
"SenderType defines the sender type of the article. Possible values: agent, "
"system, customer."
msgstr ""
"‘SenderType发件人类型’定义信件的发件人类型，可能的值有：服务人员、系统、客"
"户。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3091
msgid ""
"'TimeUnit' the time invested in the current ticket article expressed in "
"seconds, minutes, hours, etc."
msgstr "‘时间单位’花费在当前工单信件上的时间，按秒、分钟或小时等表示。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3095
msgid ""
"'DynamicField_NameX' where DynamicField_ is a required prefix and NameX is "
"the name of a Dynamic Field to be set in the new ticket (on ticket level, "
"not article levels)."
msgstr ""
"‘DynamicField_NameX’这里DynamicField_是必需的前缀，NameX是在新工单（在工单级"
"而不是信件级）设置的动态字段的名称。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3100
msgid ""
"'LinkAs' to define the new ticket relation with originator ticket, from the "
"new ticket point of view, for example Normal, Parent, Child etc."
msgstr ""
"‘LinkAs链接为’用来定义新工单与原始工单的关系，从新工单角度看，有普通（链"
"接）、父（链接）、子（链接）等等。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3107
msgid "Sets the customer of a process ticket. Example:"
msgstr "设置一个流程工单的客户。例如："

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3110
#, no-wrap
