"end, for further information please refer to the chapter about <link linkend="
"\"external-backends\">external back-ends</link>."
msgstr ""
"你可以搜索一个已注册的客户联系人，或者通过点击他们的姓名来编辑他们的设置。你"
"还可以修改客户后端，进一步信息请参考 <link linkend=\"external-backends\">外部"
