"linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:Frontend::Customer:CustomerGroupSupport"
"\">CustomerGroupSupport</link>来实现。使用参数<link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Frontend::Customer:CustomerGroupAlwaysGroups"
"\">CustomerGroupAlwaysGroups</link>你可以指定一个新添加的客户联系人的默认组，"
"以便每个新帐户会被自动添加到这些组中。"

