#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:38
msgid ""
"The Actions in the side bar at the left of the screen describes two "
"possibilities: Article and Ticket, each one has it's own dropdown selection "
"of dynamic fields."
