msgstr "可能的值：强制。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:344
msgid ""
"List of values to choose. If used, a new value is necessary to specify the "
"Key (internal value) and the Value (display value)."
msgstr "选择值的列表。如果使用了，一个新值需要指定键（内部值）和值（显示值）。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:353
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:431
