#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:363
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:441
msgid ""
"If this option is activated an extra value is defined to show as a \"-\" in "
"the list of possible values. This special value is empty internally."
msgstr ""
"如果激活了这个选项，在可能的值之外会定义一个额外的值，显示为“-”，这个特殊值在"
