"你还要指定："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:713
msgid ""
"Encoding (such as utf-8, latin1, iso-8859-1, cp1250, etc) for the SOAP "
"message."
msgstr "SOAP消息的编码（如utf-8、latin1、iso-8859-1、cp1250等等）"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:719
msgid ""
"SOAPAction Header: you can use this to send an empty or filled SOAPAction "
"header. Set to \"No\" and the SOAPAction header on the SOAP message will be "
"an empty string, or set to \"Yes\" to send the SOAP action in "
"Namespace#Action format and define the separator (typically \"/\" for .Net "
"web services and \"#\" for the REST)."
msgstr ""
"SOAP动作头：你可以使用这个来发送一个空的或填满的SOAPAction头。设置为“否”且"
"SOAP消息中的SOAP动作头会是一个空的字符串，或者设置为“是”以发送‘命名空间’#‘动"
"作’格式的SOAP动作并定义分隔符（通常.NET WEB服务是“/”，REST是“#”）。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:728
msgid ""
"Authentication: to set the authentication mechanism, set to \"-\" to not use "
"any authentication or select one from the list and the detail fields will "
"appear."
msgstr ""
"身份认证：设置身份认证机制，设置为“-”不使用任何身份认证，或从列表中选择一个身"
"份认证后会出现相关的详细字段。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:736
msgid ""
"Currently only the \"BasicAuth\" (HTTP) authentication mechanism is "
"implemented. You can decide whether or not to use it depending on the Remote "
"System configuration. If used, you must provide the User Name and the "
"Password to access the remote system."
msgstr ""
"目前只实现了“HTTP基本认证”机制。你可以根据远程系统配置决定是否要用它。如果要"
"使用“HTTP基本认证”，你必须提供用户名和密码来访问远程系统。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><warning><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:744
