msgstr " 删除原文档中任何题为“注记”的章节。这些章节可能是之针对原文档的。"

#. type: Content of: <appendix><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/fdl.xml:271
msgid ""
"Do not retitle any existing section as \"Endorsements\" or to conflict in "
"title with any Invariant Section."
msgstr "不要把任何已有章节标题改为“注记”，或改为与固定章节有冲突的标题。"

#. type: Content of: <appendix><section><para>
#: en/content/fdl.xml:277
