#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:233
msgid "Step 6: Apply the database changes"
msgstr "步骤6：应用数据库修改"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:236
msgid "Step 6.1: Database schema update"
msgstr "步骤6.1：数据库schema升级"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:239
msgid "MySQL:"
msgstr "MySQL："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:243
msgid ""
"Note: new tables created in the MySQL UPGRADING process will be created with "
"the default table storage engine set in your MySQL server.  In MySQL 5.5 the "
"new default type is <literal>InnoDB</literal>.  If existing tables, e.g. "
"\"users\", have the table storage engine e.g. <literal>MyISAM</literal>, "
"then an error will be displayed when creating the foreign key constraints.  "
"In this case we recommend to switch all tables to <literal>InnoDB</literal> "
"with the console command <command>bin/otrs.Console.pl Maint::Database::"
"MySQL::InnoDBMigration</command>."
msgstr ""
"注意：在MySQL升级过程中会在默认的表存储引擎创建新表。在MySQL 5.5中，新的默认"
"存储引擎是 <literal>InnoDB</literal>。如果现有的表如‘users’表的表存储引擎是"
"<literal>MyISAM</literal>，则在创建外键约束时会报错。在这种情况下，我们推荐将"
"所有的表切换到<literal>InnoDB</literal>引擎，可通过执行命令行脚本切换："
"<command>bin/otrs.Console.pl Maint::Database::MySQL::InnoDBMigration</"
"command>。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:254
msgid ""
"Any problems with regards to the storage engine will be reported by the "
"<filename>bin/otrs.Console.pl Maint::Database::Check</filename> command, so "
"please run it to check for possible issues."
msgstr ""
"任何与存储引擎相关的问题都可以通过命令检查出来：<filename>bin/otrs.Console."
"pl Maint::Database::Check</filename>，所以请运行这个命令来检查可能的问题。"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:259
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> cd /opt/otrs/\n"
"shell> cat scripts/DBUpdate-to-5.mysql.sql | mysql -p -f -u root otrs\n"
"shell> bin/otrs.Console.pl Maint::Database::Check\n"
msgstr ""
"shell> cd /opt/otrs/\n"
"shell> cat scripts/DBUpdate-to-5.mysql.sql | mysql -p -f -u root otrs\n"
"shell> bin/otrs.Console.pl Maint::Database::Check\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:268
msgid "PostgreSQL:"
msgstr "PostgreSQL："

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:271
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> cd /opt/otrs/\n"
"shell> cat scripts/DBUpdate-to-5.postgresql.sql | psql --set ON_ERROR_STOP=on --single-transaction otrs otrs\n"
msgstr ""
"shell> cd /opt/otrs/\n"
"shell> cat scripts/DBUpdate-to-5.postgresql.sql | psql --set ON_ERROR_STOP=on --single-transaction otrs otrs\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
