#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:190
msgid "Installing OTRS on a Red Hat Enterprise Linux or CentOS system"
msgstr "在Red Hat Enterprise Linux或CentOS系统上安装OTRS"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:193
msgid ""
"This section describes the installation of our RPM package on a Red Hat "
"Enterprise Linux (RHEL) or CentOS server. For OTRS 3.3 and up, RHEL 6 or "
"CentOS 6 is a requirement, version 5 is not supported."
msgstr ""
"本节描述了在Red Hat Enterprise Linux或CentOS系统上安装OTRS的过程。OTRS 3.3及"
"后续版本需要RHEL 6或CentOS 6，版本5不支持。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:200
msgid ""
"You can use OTRS using different database back-ends: <application>MySQL</"
"application>, <application>PostgreSQL</application> or <application>Oracle</"
"application>. The most popular database to deploy OTRS on is MySQL.  This "
"chapter shows the steps you need to take to configure MySQL on a RHEL-based "
"server.  Of course you can install the database on a dedicated database "
"server if needed for scalability or other purposes."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用不同的数据库后端：<application>MySQL</application>、"
"<application>PostgreSQL</application>或<application>Oracle</application>。部"
"署OTRS最流行的数据库是MySQL。本节描述了在基于RHEL的服务器上配置MySQL需要的步"
"骤。当然如果你有伸缩性或其它方面的需要，也可以将数据库安装到一台单独的数据库"
"服务器上。"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:210
#, no-wrap
msgid "[root@otrs-centos6 ~]# yum -y install mysql-server\n"
msgstr "[root@otrs-centos6 ~]# yum -y install mysql-server\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:229
msgid ""
"Now execute <command>systemctl start mysqld</command> to re-start the "
"database server and activate these changes. Then run <command>/usr/bin/"
"mysql_secure_installation</command> and follow the on-screen instructions to "
"set a database root password, remove anonymous access and remove the test "
"database."
msgstr ""
"现在执行命令<command>systemctl start mysqld</command>来重启数据库服务器并激活"
"刚才的修改内容。然后运行命令<command>/usr/bin/mysql_secure_installation</"
"command>并根据窗口提示来设置数据库的root用户密码、移除匿名访问和移除test数据"
"库。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:239
msgid ""
"Install OTRS with via the command line using <command>yum</command>. This "
"will also pull in some dependencies such as the Apache web server and some "
"Perl modules. Make sure you copied the OTRS RPM file to the current "
"directory."
msgstr ""
"使用<command>yum</command>通过命令行来安装OTRS，它还会拉入一些依赖包如Apache "
"WEB服务器和一些Perl模块。确保你已经将OTRS RPM文件复制到了当前目录。"

