#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:71
msgid ""
"It is also no problem if you have installed some additional features or "
"custom developments on your OTRS.  You just need to take care that all of "
"your installed packages are also compatible with Unix based systems. For "
"packages provided by OTRS this is the case."
msgstr ""
"如果你安装了一些附加功能或对OTRS进行了定制开发也没有问题。你只需注意所有安装"
"的软件也能与Unix类的系统兼容就可以了，由OTRS提供的软件包就是这样。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:76
msgid "Enable remote access for the PostgreSQL database of target system"
msgstr "允许目标系统PostgreSQL数据库的远程访问"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:78
msgid ""
"The OTSRCloneDB script will copy the database data over the network, so we "
"need to enable remote access to the database. The setup is different for the "
"different databases, we will describe opening remote access for a PostgreSQL "
"database here."
msgstr ""
"OTRSCloneDB脚本通过网络复制数据库的数据，所以我们需要允许到数据库的远程访问。"
"不同的数据库设置方法不一样，我们在这里描述的是打开PostgreSQL数据库的远程访"
"问。"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:81
msgid ""
"After logging into your target system via SSH you need to change into the "
"postgresql directory:"
msgstr "通过SSH登录到目标系统后，切换到postgresql目录："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:85
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:416
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> cd /etc/postgresql/9.4/main\n"
"shell> vi postgresql.conf\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"shell> cd /etc/postgresql/9.4/main\n"
"shell> vi postgresql.conf\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:90
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:106
msgid "Add the following line at the end of the file:"
msgstr "将下列行添加到文件末尾："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:94
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:425
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"listen_addresses = '*'\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"listen_addresses = '*'\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:98
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:114
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:429
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:445
msgid "Save the file."
msgstr "保存文件"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:102
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:433
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> vi pg_hba.conf\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"shell> vi pg_hba.conf\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:110
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:441
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"host all all  0.0.0.0/0 md5\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"host all all  0.0.0.0/0 md5\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:117
msgid "Restart your PostgreSQL server:"
msgstr "重启PostgreSQL服务器"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:121
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:452
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> service postgresql restart\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"shell> service postgresql restart\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:126
msgid "Stop OTRS services"
msgstr "停止OTRS服务"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:128
msgid "Stop all running services of your target system:"
msgstr "停止目标系统所有运行的服务："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:132
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> service cron stop\n"
"shell> service apache2 stop\n"
"shell> su - otrs\n"
"shell> cd /opt/otrs/\n"
"shell> bin/Cron.sh stop\n"
"shell> bin/otrs.Daemon.pl -a stop\n"
"shell> exit\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"shell> service cron stop\n"
"shell> service apache2 stop\n"
"shell> su - otrs\n"
"shell> cd /opt/otrs/\n"
"shell> bin/Cron.sh stop\n"
"shell> bin/otrs.Daemon.pl -a stop\n"
"shell> exit\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:143
msgid ""
"Drop the existing database of your target system to have an empty database "
"for the clone data"
msgstr "删除目标系统现有的数据库，为克隆数据腾空数据库"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:145
msgid ""
"The OTRSCloneDB script will not remove the data in the existing otrs "
"database of the target system, so we need to do this manually:"
msgstr ""
"OTRSCloneDB脚本不会移除目标系统存在的otrs数据库的数据，所以我们需要手动删除："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:148
msgid "Change the user to the postgresql user:"
msgstr "切换到postgresql用户："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:152
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> su - postgres\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"shell> su - postgres\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:156
msgid "Drop the existing otrs database:"
msgstr "删除已有的otrs数据库："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:160
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> dropdb otrs\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"shell> dropdb otrs\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:164
msgid "Create a new otrs database for the otrs user:"
msgstr "为otrs用户创建一个新的otrs数据库："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:168
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> createdb --owner=otrs --encoding=utf8 otrs\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"shell> createdb --owner=otrs --encoding=utf8 otrs\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:172
msgid "Go back to root user:"
msgstr "返回到root用户："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:176
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> exit\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"shell> exit\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:181
msgid "Get the PostgreSQL password of your database"
msgstr "获取数据库的PostgreSQL密码"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:183
msgid "Change into the OTRS directory of your target system:"
msgstr "进入目标系统的OTRS目录："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:187
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> cd /opt/otrs\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"shell> cd /opt/otrs\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:191
msgid "and take a look at the configuration file of your target system:"
msgstr "查看目录系统的配置文件："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:195
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> less Kernel/Config.pm\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"shell> less Kernel/Config.pm\n"
"                "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:199
msgid "You will find your database password if you scroll down a bit:"
msgstr "你往下拉一点就能找到你的数据库密码："

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><figure><title>
#: en/content/installation/windows.xml:203
